Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600
Set Padding 10
Set Margin 10
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Type "./turbocrunch"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "2 + 2 * (3 + 4)"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1s

Ctrl+N
Sleep 1s
Ctrl+N
Sleep 1s
Ctrl+N
Sleep 1s

Ctrl+T
Sleep 1s
Type "sin(pi/4)"
Enter
Sleep 1s


Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
